sentences.en: They feel invisible, so they cede responsibility.
sentences.cn: 他们觉得别人查不到自己，所以就置责任义务于不顾。

sentences.en: Maybe, but I'm not ready to cede the 21st century to China just yet.
sentences.cn: 也许吧。但我还不准备把21世纪拱手让给中国。

sentences.en: America was reluctant to cede any legal power to a supranational authority.
sentences.cn: 美国方面不愿将法律权利交付给某种超国家权威。
